This paper deals with reinforcement learning algorithms and their optimization in high-dimensional spaces. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of dimensionality reduction techniques, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) applications. The paper also discusses the performance of the agent's policy, which falls under the sub-category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the optimization of control, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY).
